{
  "stem": "8786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were taken out to the Russian front, climbing huge mountains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Huge mountains means we had to pick up ammunitions, 40, 50 kilo-- not pound, kilo-- which equals to about 90 pounds, I would say.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes two boys with one huge case of ammunition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to go up not on a straight level, but mountains, between trees.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was pulling down and it was somebody fall down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and actually, we had guides, guards who were pretty brutal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to schlep this out or carry it out between the two armies, in other words, into the most dangerous spots.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were supposed to deliver these.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you also had to dig ditches for the Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And many, many times we were in very dangerous positions, where the Russians saw us and they-- they were just throwing in mines.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember one Saturday afternoon a mine just exploded not far from me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] This was in-- and we were up on those mountains in Poland, actually it's the other part of the-- other side of the Hungarian border.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The name of this town was Vorokhta and Delyatyn and Mykulychyn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "These were towns which I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And huge mountains, beautiful, high mountains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it was such a job to walk up those mountains, I said to myself, never do I-- they are beautiful mountains if you go there now for a-- for a vacation place.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we were-- we were terribly tired from those-- climbing up those mountains and schlepping.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We also had to take up over there [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] nailed wires.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I recall this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barbed-- barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Hungarian army wanted to keep the Russian tanks-- these are supposed to hold them back.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
